      <title>经济摇摇欲坠之际，交易员预计欧洲央行将降息半个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/traders-put-half-point-ecb-rate-cut-in-play-as-economy-teeters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，欧洲央行决策者在降低借贷成本的同时警告称，经济增长面临风险，交易员们因此加大了对欧洲央行 12 月份将需要大幅降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/traders-put-half-point-ecb-rate-cut-in-play-as-economy-teeters</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:27:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国 ETF 与 Cathie Wood 并列成为美国最大的财富破坏者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/china-etfs-join-cathie-wood-s-as-biggest-wealth-destroyers-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于那些前所未有地向中国股票 ETF 投入数十亿美元资金的交易员来说，我们需要注意的是：这种策略不仅容易出现重大逆转，而且在过去十年甚至更长的时间里，还让一批不合时宜的投资者损失惨重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/china-etfs-join-cathie-wood-s-as-biggest-wealth-destroyers-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:09:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2025 年展望：美国房屋建筑商信心创四个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/us-homebuilder-sentiment-reaches-four-month-high-on-2025-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本月，美国房屋建筑商的信心跃升至四个月高位，抵押贷款利率下降的前景激发了人们对未来一年新房需求的乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/us-homebuilder-sentiment-reaches-four-month-high-on-2025-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
