      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 12:48:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国零售和劳动力数据强劲，日元跌至关键的 150 水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/yen-falls-to-key-150-level-sparking-more-intervention-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强劲的美国消费者支出和劳动力数据导致交易员减少对美联储明年降息的押注，导致日元兑美元跌破 150 的关键心理关口，从而推高了美元兑主要货币的汇率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/yen-falls-to-key-150-level-sparking-more-intervention-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 12:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石信贷部门已成为其主要业务，推动利润增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/blackstone-s-credit-arm-is-now-its-top-business-fueling-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石公司 (Blackstone Inc.) 公布第三季度利润增长，其信贷部门受到投资者现金流入的推动，成为该公司资产规模最大的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/blackstone-s-credit-arm-is-now-its-top-business-fueling-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 10:56:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
